Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kau tahu. Dia bilang padaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.65,0:02:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Lihat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Dia keren sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Dia potong rambut!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}- Kudengar dia di sini dapat beasiswa!\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}- Itu jarang terjadi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Mereka bilang dia bahkan\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}pernah mengalahkan Oguri Cap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Sungguh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Halo, Pelatih.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Halo, March...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa jadwal latihan hari ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa? Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}- Fundamental dan pelatihan gerbang.\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}- Paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku akan ganti baju.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}March, apa suasana hatimu sedang bagus?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa kelihatan? Kurasa begitu, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kau tak pernah bilang "halo" padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Setelah kalah di Derby Tokai,\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}kau terlihat sedih...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ya, kemarin aku telepon Oguri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.88,0:03:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Jadilah yang terbaik di Jepang, Oguri Cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kurasa aku memberinya semangat,\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}jadi aku tak boleh berdiam diri saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Giliranku untuk menuju gunung berikutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku senang kau berhenti galau\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}tepat waktu untuk ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:03:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Gifu Okan Sho?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Balapan terdaftar\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}sepanjang 1.900 meter lintasan tanah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Di antara pesertanya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}ada pemenang Derby Tokai, Yamano Thousand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:15.76,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kemenangan di pertandingan ulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Itu gunung yang sempurna untuk dituju, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kau pelatih yang baik, tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Suasana hatimu benar-benar bagus hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Jadi, Gifu Okan Sho, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Itu seperti balapan\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}yang menentukan raja dari Gifu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kuberi komentar itu\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}nilai tiga dari seratus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Jadi, kapan balapan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tanggal 10 Juli.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa? Tidak mungkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Itu hari yang sama dengan lomba Oguri,\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Takamatsunomiya Hai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ya, aku tahu. Kebetulan sekali, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.71,0:04:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku harus bagaimana?\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku mau menonton keduanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Haruskah bawa TV ke Arena Balap Kasamatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:04:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Jangan bercanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa? Itu tak ada salahnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}- Maaf, aku tak...\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}- Memperhatikan? Ya, hati-hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Benar juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:13.48,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kau hanya peduli Oguri sialan itu.
