Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Kini, pembalap berikutnya\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}yang memasuki kandang adalah{\i0}
