Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:33.70,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Sejak Oguri ke ibu kota, aku hanya
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}menang satu kali dan kalah lima kali.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Yamano Thousand punya empat kemenangan\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}dan dua kali juara dua.{\i0}
